org.sd.cluster.job
Class WorkBatch

java.lang.Object
  org.sd.cluster.job.WorkBatch

public class WorkBatch
extends java.lang.Object

Container for a batch of work.

A batch is constructed by collecting new units of work or by restoring itself from a persisted batch for continued processing.

Author:
Spence Koehler
